==English==
===Alternative spellings===
* [[ilooy]]

===Etymology===
Yiddish [[עילוי]], from Hebrew [[עילוי|עִילּוּי]] (''‘ilúi'', "prodigy").

===Noun===
'''iluy'''

#A [[Talmud]]ic [[prodigy]].
#A [[boy wonder]].

